{
  "texts": [
    "The latter is enabled via the arXiv python API.",
    "We used a similar approach as the \"StuffDocumentsChain\" in Lang-Chain to refine the explanations.",
    "First, we select the most related literature excerpts using maximal marginal relevance search (MMR).",
    "Then, the text excerpts are \"stuffed\" to a specialized prompt to generate the final explanation.",
    "We utilize the chain-of-thought prompting approach 50 where a series of intermediate steps and examples are provided in the prompt to improve the output's interpretability."
  ]
}